text: Oswald Probst was an archer from Austria. Probst competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics.Oswald PROBST He was born on 9 July 1935 and died on 15 July 2015.Oswald Probst == References == Category:1935 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Austrian archers Category:Olympians for Austria Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
